{"tid":854892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Call車APP公司Grab獲微軟入股 拓大數據AI合作","createTime":"2018-10-09T16:27:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T16:27:27.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"91c23465e8f9d38b96a68f08a8feeb1f33dbc890","tid":854892,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T16:27:27.000Z","msg":"微軟（Microsoft）公佈，投資新加坡叫車app公司Grab，作為策略夥伴的一部分，微軟未有公佈入股金額。英國金融時報引述消息指出，微軟入股Grab金額約2億美元，其估值達到120億美元（折合936億港元），雙方皆拒評。<br />\n<br />\n該兩家公司將會於科技項目進行合作，例如大數據、AI等等，Grab將使用微軟的產品，包括Azure雲計算服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181009/58773587\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181009%2F58773587&d=9muGD2B2HDW9YKzsh4glQdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=8ecd3861\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181009%2F58773587&h=9363b777\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181009/58773587</a>"}]}